column1: Summary of Core ICT Indicators for Establishments Under Business Process Management (BPM) Activities: Philippines

column4: 2013 Establishments with computer and other hardware
column7: 2013 Employees using computer routinely at work
column8: 2013 Employees using computer with internet connection routinely at work
column12: 2013 Establishments with wired local area network
column13: 2013 Establishments with wireless local area network
column15: 2013 Establishments with e-commerce via the internet
column16: 2013 Establishments with e-commerce via computer networks other than the internet
column17: 2013 Establishments with business transaction via cellular mobile phone
column18: 2013 Establishments which used the internet for finance accounting and auditing
column19: 2013 Establishments which used the internet for internal or external recruitment
column20: 2013 Establishments which used the internet for staff training
column21: 2013 Establishments which used the internet for sharing or distribution of information within the establishment
column22: 2013 Establishments which used the internet for sharing or distribution of information with other organizations
column23: 2013 Establishments which used the internet for obtaining information from other organizations
column24: 2013 Establishments which used the internet for obtaining information from government organizations
column25: 2013 Establishments which used the internet for downloading or requesting government forms
column26: 2013 Establishments which used the internet for completing forms on-line or sending completed forms
column27: 2013 Establishments which used the internet for making on-line payments to government corporations
